# Single-maintainer repo today; the file exists to:
#   - flag PRs that touch sensitive paths (release pipeline, FFI,
#     security policy, installer) for explicit review even by the
#     maintainer
#   - signal review expectations to outside contributors
#   - stay correct when collaborators are added later

